February 5th

Never so keen on cleaning and cleaning, the house finally forced out of a neat cell.

It is said that some journalists have to pack up like an obsessive compulsive before writing articles. I have never had such a hobby before. I have to browse Taobao before writing and revising articles, but recently I am not very good at placing orders for logistics. This habit has been abruptly interrupted, i had to learn how to clean.

It's a little hard to understand why housewives have a mysterious obsession with the cleanliness of their homes. Stay at home, do housework can be the only exercise, once a day is not very good?

Mopping the floor with disinfectant every two days is a bit of a nervous breakdown, a bit of a throwback to childhood dental domination.

I had a lot of perfumes in my collection, and my friend thought it would be a waste of time, so he picked a few inexpensive Air freshener. It's a prerequisite. After mopping the floor, the smell was so overwhelming that I picked it up on the table as Air freshener perfume and sprayed it twice -- as if it were a perfume

It's a Kappa sportswear perfume. I don't care what the middle and back notes are, the top notes are full of the scent of Patchouli.

So in disinfection water and Patchouli Zhengqi water under the double blessing, soaring.

February 6th, across the 7th

A lot of people stayed up all night. I division out of 7 little brother and sister reporters and an intern little brother, at least three did not sleep, three or four o'clock still throw links to the group.
